{"tid":1243063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我用我方法] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合","createTime":"2019-06-19T09:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T04:35:39.000Z","uid":216800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"261bfc89aa70c706902a83d27eb021fc406d1b08","tid":1243063,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"原PO : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好鬆懈!!<br />\n有義士花費龐大精力搜集到既資料 唔好令佢白費!!!<br />\n騎士仔我提議 一人一個開用佢個PO名 + 佢PO既LINK 用自己帳號開一次 然後自己推自己<br />\n目的令版面佔多數 (如果見到有4-5個佔左版面 請各自自律唔好再開)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係洗板 雖然係令大家造成困擾 雖然咁做會好ON9<br />\n但騎士仔我覺得一個PO 係唔夠入眾眼簾<br />\n而且原PO入邊好多POST推晒上黎會好容易造成混亂<br />\n最好一個POST長期被置頂 入邊有晒咁多樣野 方便大家!!!<br />\n而分身PO只係引導去原PO!!<br />\n<br />\n唔洗推我 我自推<br />\n想推就去原PO推"},{"pid":"598691236a4e291d21629abe7b94644a16fb6633","tid":1243063,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8fdb1bee42067e6e43adb9836840e9358bece8","tid":1243063,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee90c0281cffe69aafb9e069ae3ec650c313076","tid":1243063,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a37d23184d8fbe5ee3ec0f8df4cfeaed7c1766b","tid":1243063,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baaf056191d577d69f383376e605af025f0e0af","tid":1243063,"uid":32655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0837f58